{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Legend of the Galactic Heroes'' media}} {{Cleanup|reason=This article may be better off as a template|date=September 2015}}
This is a list of media related to the long-running series '''''[[Legend of the Galactic Heroes]]'''''.
== Main stories ==
